{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2df0dba580","title":"中共内邱县委员会关于李如松右派问题的批复","origin":"根据文件翻印件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"274659e1d2","index":0,"year":1979,"month":3,"day":25,"articleId":"2df0dba580"}],"tags":[{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6a2babf9a5","type":"title","text":"中共内邱县委员会关于李如松右派问题的批复","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"},{"id":"2ca8ffca71","type":"appellation","text":"文教局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"},{"id":"c5b0dbd3f2","type":"paragraph","text":"根据你局报来李如松的复查材料及处理意见，一九五八年李因右派言论被划为右派分子，受开除公职，劳动教养处分。经县委落实政策领导小组一九七九年三月二十四日研究：根据中共中央【1978】55号文件精神，李旧军人成分，思想落后，对新社会有不满情绪，说过一些错话。但未公开扩散，故对李的右派问题予以改正。撤消原处分，恢复政治名誉，恢复公职，恢复原级别（月工资73元），自一九七八年十月起执行。望通知其所在单位和本人，并在会上公布执行。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"},{"id":"7efa277505","type":"appellation","text":"此  复","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"},{"id":"da520937c1","type":"paragraph","text":" 中国共产党内丘县委员会落实政策办公室一九七九年三月二十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"},{"id":"bf40f38646","type":"appellation","text":"抄送：组织部、宣传部","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"},{"id":"dd2e4d8b19","type":"subtitle","text":"中共内邱县委员会（批复）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"},{"id":"1a7befb989","type":"subtitle","text":"（1979）355号","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"},{"id":"82558b3edb","type":"appellation","text":"文教局：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"},{"id":"63c40b59ec","type":"paragraph","text":"根据你局报来刘岳华的复查材料及处理意见，一九五八年刘因受其爱人李如松右派问题株连，失去工作，经县委落实政策领导小组一九七九年五月廿七日研究：根据中共中央【1978】55号文件精神，刘原系国家正式教员，确系因受其爱人李如松右派问题株连而失去工作，现李的右派问题已经改正，故恢复刘的公职及原级别（月工资29.5元）。根据本人要求，同意办理退休手续。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"},{"id":"ff0a9eefff","type":"appellation","text":"此  复","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"},{"id":"a3223c43d7","type":"paragraph","text":" 中国共产党内丘县委员会落实政策办公室一九七九年五月廿八日","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"},{"id":"59e221af5f","type":"appellation","text":"抄送：组织部、宣传部","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"},{"id":"c2cacf212e","type":"subtitle","text":"李汝松老先生的起义人员证明书","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"},{"id":"2d03fbf06b","type":"subtitle","text":"北内邱起字第003号","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"},{"id":"199bc07378","type":"paragraph","text":"李汝松同志，原系国民党华北汽车第一团连长少校，于一九四九年一月十日在北京参加傅作义部队起义，特此证明。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"},{"id":"290ab032ca","type":"paragraph","text":" 中国人民解放军北京军区一九八五年七月二十日","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580"}],"page":{"id":"e0dc14cff5","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2df0dba580","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}